#. <section class="sutta" id="sn7.20"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn7.20:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 7"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 7"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn7.20:0.2"
msgid "2. Upāsakavagga"
msgstr "2. Lay Followers"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn7.20:0.3"
msgid "20. Bhikkhakasutta"
msgstr "20. A Beggar"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn7.20:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ."
msgstr "At Sāvatthī."

msgctxt "sn7.20:1.2"
msgid ""
"Atha kho bhikkhako brāhmaṇo yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā "
"bhagavatā saddhiṃ sammodi."
msgstr ""
"Then a begging brahmin went up to the Buddha, and exchanged greetings with "
"him."

msgctxt "sn7.20:1.3"
msgid ""
"Sammodanīyaṃ kathaṃ sāraṇīyaṃ vītisāretvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. Ekamantaṃ "
"nisinno kho bhikkhako brāhmaṇo bhagavantaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr ""
"When the greetings and polite conversation were over, he sat down to one "
"side and said to the Buddha:"

msgctxt "sn7.20:1.4"
msgid ""
"“ahampi kho, bho gotama, bhikkhako, bhavampi bhikkhako, idha no kiṃ "
"nānākaraṇan”ti?"
msgstr ""
"“Master Gotama, both you and I are beggars. What, then, is the difference "
"between us?”"

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn7.20:2.1"
msgid "“Na tena bhikkhako hoti,"
msgstr "“You don’t become a beggar"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn7.20:2.2"
msgid "yāvatā bhikkhate pare;"
msgstr "just by begging from others."

# See BB for readings.
#. <br>
msgctxt "sn7.20:2.3"
msgid "Vissaṃ dhammaṃ samādāya,"
msgstr "Someone who has accepted domestic responsibilities"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn7.20:2.4"
msgid "bhikkhu hoti na tāvatā."
msgstr "has not yet become a mendicant."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts2ed" id="pts2ed1.393"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "sn7.20:3.1"
msgid "Yodha puññañca pāpañca,"
msgstr "But one living a spiritual life"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn7.20:3.2"
msgid "bāhitvā brahmacariyaṃ;"
msgstr "who has shunned both good and bad,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn7.20:3.3"
msgid "Saṅkhāya loke carati,"
msgstr "having considered, they live in this world:"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn7.20:3.4"
msgid "sa ve bhikkhūti vuccatī”ti."
msgstr "that’s who’s called a mendicant.”"

#. </p></blockquote><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "sn7.20:4.1"
msgid "Evaṃ vutte, bhikkhako brāhmaṇo bhagavantaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr "When he had spoken, the begging brahmin said to the Buddha:"

msgctxt "sn7.20:4.2"
msgid "“abhikkantaṃ, bho gotama, abhikkantaṃ, bho gotama … pe …"
msgstr "“Excellent, Master Gotama! Excellent! …"

msgctxt "sn7.20:4.3"
msgid ""
"upāsakaṃ maṃ bhavaṃ gotamo dhāretu ajjatagge pāṇupetaṃ saraṇaṃ gatan”ti."
msgstr ""
"From this day forth, may Master Gotama remember me as a lay follower who has "
"gone for refuge for life.”"
